he'd love to do a ceremonial puck drop).\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her beloved Islanders\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"her uncle\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"Jon\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"a co\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"owner\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"a ceremonial puck drop\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Occasionally, she catches Saturday Night Live (she watched Caitlin Clark, and would love to be invited, hint hint).\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday Night Live\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But travel can be difficult.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why Ledecky hasmostlyseen the world through the eyes of international swimming competition, as she admitted to us with a chuckle.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"the eyes\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"international swimming competition\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"a chuckle\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since London (in 2012), all of my international travel has been for swim meets,\\\" Ledecky noted, \\\"and I have done a lot of them.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1199, 