"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Occasionally, she noted, she will add a few days at the end of business trips in order to explore the city she just dominated in, but \\\"is not someone who takes long, extensive breaks at the end of seasons\\\".\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"business trips\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"long, extensive breaks\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"seasons\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That relentlessness is what's allowed Ledecky to reach an early peak and stay awhile.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That relentlessness\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"an early peak\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, the now-27-year-old has formalized a long-time reliance with Core Power into an official partnership, as she chases recovery throughout the training process.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long-time reliance\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"Core Power\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"an official partnership\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"the training process\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Competing at the Olympic level does not come without a strong understanding of how to recover and refuel,\\\" Ledecky stated.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic level\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong understanding\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been at it a long time, and I learn more and more every year.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From an early age, I learned that recovery and getting those nutrients to refuel after a hard practice or a hard race is really crucial.\\\"\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"those nutrients\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"a hard practice\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"a hard race\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite that \\\"long\\\" time and lengthy history of international stardom, each time Ledecky lands on Olympic soil, she still has the same overwhelmed feeling on Day 1.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that \\\"long\\\" time\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"lengthy history\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"international stardom\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic soil\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"the same overwhelmed feeling\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each time I walk into the Olympic Village for the first time, that's when it really hits me that I have made it back,\\\" Ledecky noted wistfully, as she charges forward for her fourth appearance.\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4943929753163288e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth appearance\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being among all these different athletes from all over the world, all different sports, coming together in this one moment in this little village is pretty amazing.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all these different athletes\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"this one moment\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"this little village\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pretty amazing to people watch and see everyone in the cafeteria getting ready for their competition, going off to their different buses to their different venues ... to be a part of that is pretty surreal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"the cafeteria\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"their competition\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"their different buses\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"their different venues\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans of Ledecky's know she's more than just a \\\"part of it\\\"; she's a centerpiece.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a \\\"part\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"a centerpiece\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And thanks to relentless training, she's poised to once again show off on the world stage (and then, if she has time, see that world a little bit and bask in it).\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"relentless training\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3204}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"that world\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loading recommendations\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations \\u00c2\\u00a9 2025Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personalized content recommendations\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"All Rights\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The content\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"this site\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3491}, {\"ngram\": \"entertainment and educational purposes\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Minute Media or its affiliates and related brands.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Betting and gambling content\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"individual commentators' opinions\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"Minute Media\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3683}, {\"ngram\": \"its affilia